    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克将在争议投票的阴影下举行新总统就职典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozambique-to-inaugurate-president-in-shadow-of-disputed-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹尼尔·查波将于周三宣誓就任莫桑比克新总统，他将领导一个国家，而这个国家因数月的抗议活动而支离破碎，抗议活动夺去了数百人的生命，使经济陷入瘫痪，而且很多人不认为他是合法当选的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozambique-to-inaugurate-president-in-shadow-of-disputed-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑切斯将英国买家当替罪羊无法解决西班牙住房问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/sanchez-scapegoating-uk-buyers-won-t-fix-spanish-housing-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙计划阻止外国人购买住宅物业，这可能会对度假小镇和豪宅开发商造成冲击，但对于缓解当地人住房短缺的问题却收效甚微。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/sanchez-scapegoating-uk-buyers-won-t-fix-spanish-housing-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南改革启动 国营电视台停播</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/vietnam-state-run-tv-channels-taken-off-air-as-reforms-kick-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在越南政府大力推进削减官僚主义的改革计划下，越南至少有 16 个国营电视台停止播出，最终将只留下一个国家电视台继续播出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/vietnam-state-run-tv-channels-taken-off-air-as-reforms-kick-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 04:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国放宽针对专业人士和富裕外国人的签证规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/thailand-eases-visa-rules-for-professionals-wealthy-foreigners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁本周批准修改该国签证规则，以增加对技术专业人士、投资者和富有的外国人获得长期居留许可的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/thailand-eases-visa-rules-for-professionals-wealthy-foreigners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 04:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永哲被捕后面临的法律风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/all-about-south-korean-president-yoon-s-legal-perils-after-his-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1 月 15 日，韩国总统尹锡烈因宣布短暂戒严令而被调查人员逮捕，他的法律风险进一步升级。韩国议会已于 12 月 14 日对他进行弹劾，此前议员们认为他的声明违反了宪法。尹锡烈已被剥夺总统权力，正在等待是否被免职的判决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/all-about-south-korean-president-yoon-s-legal-perils-after-his-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永哲因戒严令失败被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/south-korean-investigators-arrest-yoon-at-second-attempt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国调查人员于周三黎明前展开行动，逮捕了总统尹锡烈，就其短暂的戒严令展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/south-korean-investigators-arrest-yoon-at-second-attempt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 01:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>字节跳动的人工智能让这位大亨成为亚洲最富有的女性之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/bytedance-s-ai-makes-chinese-tycoon-one-of-asia-s-richest-women</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业家周潮男已成为全球 500 位富豪中仅有的三位中国女性亿万富翁之一。随着 TikTok 所有者字节跳动有限公司的崛起和人工智能的蓬勃发展，她跻身这一稀有女性亿万富翁俱乐部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/bytedance-s-ai-makes-chinese-tycoon-one-of-asia-s-richest-women</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 23:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
